DESCRIPTION:Friends of Lake Sammamish State Park\, welcome Bats Northwest B
	oard member and biologist Bernice Tannebaum for a Lakeside Lecture about B
	ats of Northwest\, bat boxes and luckily for anyone who attends this event
	\, the incredible depth of Bernice bat knowledge.  She was featured this s
	ummer in the Seattle Times.    The event is a free indoor event but a dona
